different markets.

00:34:23.739 --> 00:34:27.540
In response to feedback from
a bunch of our developers

00:34:27.540 --> 00:34:29.679
who had a lot of apps
or published their apps

00:34:29.679 --> 00:34:32.239
in a lot of
countries, we're also

00:34:32.239 --> 00:34:33.934
offering the developer
publishing API.

00:34:35.010 --> 00:34:37.040
So if you're a developer
with, let's say,

00:34:37.040 --> 00:34:40.219
100 apps, and each of those
apps is offered in 50 languages,

00:34:40.219 --> 00:34:42.770
and you've uploaded
all of the text,

00:34:42.770 --> 00:34:45.050
and all of the
tablet screenshots,

00:34:45.050 --> 00:34:47.500
and all the banners, for all
those different languages,

00:34:47.500 --> 00:34:49.335
it becomes kind of a
multiplicative problem.

00:34:50.360 --> 00:34:52.290
And so we thought, we
can do better than that.

00:34:52.290 --> 00:34:56.420
So we now have an API that you
can use to manage your APKs,

00:34:56.420 --> 00:34:58.582
