listing, the graphics

00:34:58.582 --> 00:34:59.540
for your store listing.

00:35:00.690 --> 00:35:02.850
And you can also manage
your in-app product

00:35:02.850 --> 00:35:05.560
catalog and alpha
and beta tests.

00:35:05.560 --> 00:35:07.930
You're able to integrate this
with whatever build system

00:35:07.930 --> 00:35:11.120
that your company
has so that you

00:35:11.120 --> 00:35:14.320
can take those assets directly
from where they are already

00:35:14.320 --> 00:35:16.750
on your servers and in
your development process

00:35:16.750 --> 00:35:18.960
and push them directly
into the Developer Console

00:35:18.960 --> 00:35:22.070
and into Google Play without
a bunch of copy and paste.

00:35:22.070 --> 00:35:24.840
So if you have a really
big operation like this,

00:35:24.840 --> 00:35:27.577
we definitely recommend
that you check this out,

00:35:27.577 --> 00:35:29.660
